com.o3dr.services.android.lib.gcs.link

Annotation Type LinkConnectionStatus.FailureCode


  • @Retention(value=SOURCE)
public static @interface LinkConnectionStatus.FailureCode
    The possible failure codes that can be retrieved from the LinkConnectionStatus.getExtras() using key LinkConnectionStatus.EXTRA_ERROR_CODE. A LinkConnectionStatus.FailureCode is guaranteed when LinkConnectionStatus.FAILED occurs.
